messages.content:
Certainly. The email template embedded in the system prompt is:
```
Subject: Your New Case ID – {case_id}

Dear {client_name},

Thank you for sharing the details of your {case_type} case. Your case has been opened with ID {case_id}. Here is a brief summary of the information we captured:

- Incident Date: {incident_date}
- Jurisdiction: {jurisdiction}
- Opposing Party: {opposing_party}
- Fact Summary: {fact_summary}

Our team will review the information and contact you shortly to discuss next steps.

Best regards,
Legal Intake Team
```
(End of email template.)
